A flattr plugin for the habari blog
===================================

Purpose
-------

Automatically add flattr buttons to blog posts

Features
--------
  * Can automatically add autosubmit link at end of post
  * Can be used inside a theme
  * Configurable large or small icon
  * Tags of the post are automatically added as tags to the flattr
  * Plugin can be configured to hide flattrs from public listing

To be implemented
-----------------
  Attributes of links
  * categories
  * language
  * description
